# ❌ Bug Report: Book Details Not Displayed

**ID:** BUG-UI-002 
**Module:** Book Store – Book Details  
**Severity:** Medium  
**Environment:**  
- Browser: Chrome/Safari  
- URL: https://demoqa.com/books?book=9781449325862  

---

## 🔥 Description:
When clicking on a book from the list on the Book Store page, the application redirects to a details page using the book's ISBN. However, the resulting page is blank, and no book details are shown.

---

## 🧪 Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open https://demoqa.com/books
2. Click on any book title (e.g., "Git Pocket Guide")
3. Observe that the new page shows no content

---

## 😵 Actual Result:
- Page loads with empty body
- No title, author, or description displayed

## ✅ Expected Result:
- Page displays full details of the selected book: title, author, description, ISBN, etc.

---

## 📸 Screenshot / Console (optional):
- https://demoqa.com/books?book=9781449325862
